1. place finger on the left most card.

2. if card´s value is larger than the value of the card to its right, swap the two cards.
  a. swap the two cards
  b. go back to step 1
  
3. else if that card´s value is smaller than the value of the card to its right, move your finger to the card to the card on the right (with the bigger number).

4. repeat steps 2-3 until your finger is on the rightmost card
